    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive condition both inside and out. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, showing only minor surface stone chips consistent with responsible road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium upholstery shows light, natural wear on the driver\u2019s bolster but remains firm and supportive, while all electronic features\u2014including the navigation, premium audio system, and dual-zone climate control\u2014function exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust, offering a smooth and responsive driving experience with crisp gear shifts and steady handling. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a fresh oil change and a full multi-point inspection performed within the last 500 miles. The tires possess approximately 70% of their tread life, and the brake pads were recently replaced. Included with the sale are two sets of keys, the original owner's manuals, and a thick folder of service receipts. This is a reliable, well-documented example that is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without any deferred maintenance.",
